{"tid":1426533,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒！ 唔支持港獨但反送中既係唔係同路人?","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:37:04.000Z","uid":3040,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"962da35b6abcba4bcb64d3fdd71fdd6d90f0a9db","tid":1426533,"uid":3040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"最近留意到一個風向就係分代唔支持港獨但反送中既同路人<br />\n<br />\n呢場反送中運動既核心價值係5大訴求，亦都係民間主流既共識，當中係唔包括港獨<br />\n<br />\n點解我地要同唔支持港獨但反送中既同路人分割?<br />\n<br />\n大家千其唔好又中共產黨既分代手段，集中5大訴求，不分化﹑不割蓆！"},{"pid":"e91b3da085ac73516a3125c53221bef6ce705c3c","tid":1426533,"uid":11448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"5大訴求始終如一<br />\nBTW我想知邊到有人講緊港獨wo"},{"pid":"170a197096b4ab56c1aa8f92dfa2677e4b02637b","tid":1426533,"uid":53604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:46:38.000Z","msg":"係，但我相信始終每個人都會得出香港需要獨立呢一個結論"},{"pid":"b67c87e9a02c25204e6772b4af8d41e636b3af1c","tid":1426533,"uid":3040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"正如Hottoys唔支持港獨，但又罷市支持反送中運動，咁值唔值得大家大大力屌?"},{"pid":"33844c53779418cb5fbaa4561ff0454b32d8c73d","tid":1426533,"uid":285413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3KpDtX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3KpDtX.png&h=625d9d04&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />霑叔的話，值得一看。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f764f61ed1a7b6824ddbfc2f1ddd0ac46985026","tid":1426533,"uid":267337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c89eb5f297069f44e5337d2db6bef155e53bcd6b","tid":1426533,"uid":3040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb5667fa26f993b9b407a64aae9b9e4d793dff